{"tid":154741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 廣東話Kyrie Irving主題曲 ] 射撚柒你 要盡快mark艾榮","createTime":"2017-03-13T13:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T05:31:46.000Z","uid":47374,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5146d6131894f9d9c5df8be6b578740a95ef23b4","tid":154741,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5X36PU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5X36PU.jpg&h=12d8b327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1820405578212412/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frealcoach%2Fvideos%2F1820405578212412%2F&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b5b48327\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1820405578212412/</a><br />\n<br />\n原片串錯字無得救，呢度講唔好意思先<br />\n但我每次改NBA主題曲都好有誠意，希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n係時候歌頌返Kyrie Irving<br />\n佢除咗係超強狀元，反勝勇士贏總冠軍<br />\n其實佢仲繼承緊父親嘅籃球夢想，<br />\n請多多支持同Share，下個到Kawhi Leonard<br />\n<br />\n原：爛泥(許志安)<br />\n詞：正宗教練<br />\n唱：Adrain Tang<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無嘢及冠軍實際 <br />\n榮哥上力 想阻佢搵邊位<br />\n被嚴密防守 手感靚無計<br />\n就算9拋佢照入 咪Q提<br />\n<br />\n佢老豆猛鼓勵佢<br />\n年輕有夢 應該勇敢爭取<br />\n大王話離隊 騎士揀咗佢<br />\n硬拼咗幾季最後完成大創舉<br />\n<br />\n十幾廿歲 佢做最佳狀元<br />\n唔L劣你 佢望見Kobe夠膽串<br />\n第一鑊嘢 佢就要擔大權<br />\n成幾十歲 佢仲去街場虐待你點算<br />\n<br />\n射L7你 要盡快mark艾榮<br />\n唔講道理 佢射到Curry無反應<br />\n撥走劣勢 要令對手現形<br />\n唔使運氣 帶住決心能夠後上反勝"},{"pid":"37f5bd945581ef533f069ba994a258899eb750ab","tid":154741,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bf1b819825b64e57f15b090890ac7122edfd9ec8","tid":154741,"uid":13810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82eb76d8242ecfb4d805b0e53f0874bf4c41e3f","tid":154741,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco